==Textile arts==
===Embroidery=== [[Chinese embroidery]] is one of the oldest extant needlework. The four major regional styles of [[Chinese embroidery]] are [[Suzhou embroidery|Suzhou]] (Su Xiu), [[Hunan]] (Xiang Xiu), [[Guangdong]] (Yue Xiu) and [[Chinese embroidery#Major styles|Sichuan]] (Shu Xiu). All of them are nominated as Chinese [[Intangible Cultural Heritage]].{{citation needed|date=August 2012}}
